{"tid":1884942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥稱防疫抗疫基金預留10億元全力搜購口罩！","createTime":"2020-02-18T03:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T15:19:11.000Z","uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ae88d2cc01e6edb70a9808e91c0bdfc778e4041d","tid":1884942,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9125889b5e6be097607fdfb296218aeeb354e2a","tid":1884942,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥出席行政會議前表示，政府正全力搜購口罩，已在防疫抗疫基金預留10億元採購，若有成效，將為政府以外人士提供口罩。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，現時為合約清潔工，發放每日一口罩，亦為全港公私營院舍提供口罩。政府昨日已啟動分發獲捐贈口罩的工作，並由她和問責局長親自派發，這項工作會持續。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">若各界人士能用自己方法買到口罩，希望他們能分享予有需要人士。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509185-20200218.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509185-20200218.htm&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=fa4e7fb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509185-20200218.htm&h=10075656\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509185-20200218.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dbde2d1a043862883fc602ed0cce6d70bf770179","tid":1884942,"uid":63113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:01:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">若各界人士能用自己方法買到口罩，希望他們能分享予有需要人士。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QY4APvg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQY4APvg.gif&h=e81d7c03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c84c47ef125eed113a92b9762d9ece77ac446bf4","tid":1884942,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:03:13.000Z","msg":"10億招標 價低者得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5288202f9dad60